name: Leaf Ring
description:
This leaf ring is hand carved out of wax and then cast in silver. The leaf shape wraps around your finger and lays flat, so it does not get in the way. It would be easy to wear on a regular basis because it would go well with other silver jewelry while the leaf motif is pretty and unique.

Materials:
Sterling Silver
Available sizes: 5, 5.5, 6, 6.5, 7, 7.5, 8, 8.5, 9
Please message me what size you would like.
Goes well with Leaf and Pyrite Earrings

name: Leaf and Stone Earrings
description:
The leaves are handmade out of silver sheet metal, and then I set either a black or green stone secured by a silver wire. They are finished with an oversized ear wire that accents the leaf shape. These earrings are easy to pair with your wardrobe because they can be easily dressed up or down.

Materials:
Sterling silver and black spinel or green peridot (Please message me which stone you prefer) 
2.3 inches long
Can easily be worn with other silver jewelry including the Byzantine Chain Bracelet

name: Pearl and Leaf Earrings
description:
These delicate earrings would be a unique finishing touch to pearl jewelry you already have because of the cast silver leaf or would be a great addition to the Trinkety and Pearl Necklace. These earrings are lightweight and easy to wear on a daily basis, and that is completely alright because they are extremely cute!

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
1.75 inches long
Would be a great finishing touch to the Trinkety and Pearl Necklace or Bracelet

name: Byzantine Chain and Labradorite Earrings
description:
These unique earrings are created by weaving silver jump rings together. This creates a three dimensional earring that is finished with a labradorite teardrop. Labradorite is what I would consider a vibrant yet neutral color. It has a blue, green, and grey coloring that would pick up what ever color you wear them with. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and labradorite
1.5 inches long
Would go great with the Byzantine Chain Necklace or Bracelet

name: Byzantine Chain Necklace
description:
This necklace is perfect for everyday wear. It is has a clean design that will go with your wardrobe. This three dimensional chain is made up of woven jump rings, making a thick chain necklace that is sturdy by still has movement. 

Materials:
Sterling Silver
18 inches long (Can be adjusted if requested)
Would go well with the Byzantine Chain Bracelet or Earrings

name: Byzantine Chain Bracelet
description:
This bracelet is perfect for everyday wear. It is has a clean design that will go with your wardrobe but has a twist with the hanging lavender charm. The bracelet is made up of woven jump rings, making a sturdy bracelet that still has movement. 

Materials:
Sterling silver
7.5 inches long
Pairs well with either Byzantine Chain Necklace or Earrings

name: Splash Cast Ring
description:
This organic ring is very special. I created the top piece with a method called splash casting where I melt silver and pour it into cool water, creating unique shapes. I then made a mold of this particular shape so I could make more them! It would be a great finishing touch that could be worn alone or stacked with bands you already own. 

Materials: 
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls 
Available sizes: 5, 5.5, 6, 6.5, 7, 7.5, 8, 8.5, 9 
Please message me what size you would like.

name: Trinkety Pearl Bracelet
description:
Each component is carved from wax and then cast in silver. I then connected all the components to create a collected feel, as if you were walking threw nature picking up leaves, branches, and flowers. I then added pearls, one of my favorite materials. This creates a one of a kind bracelet that would be a great addition to any jewelry collection.

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
7.5 inches long (Can be adjusted if requested)
Looks great with the Trinkety Pearl Chain Necklace and Pearl Post Earrings

name: Leaf and Pyrite Earrings
description:
This is a great earring that combines natural cast leaf elements and edgy earwires that are oversized and wrapped with small pyrite beads. It creates an attractive and exceptional pair of earrings. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and pyrite 
2.25 inches long

name: Lavender Studs
description:
These cute studs are great little earrings that are simple, sweet, and easy to wear on a regular basis. 

Materials:
Sterling silver
.65 inches long
These earrings look great with the Trinkety Chain Necklace

name: Infinity Link and Pearl Earrings
description:
These earrings would be a great finishing touch to any outfit because of their simple yet unique design. I added three pearls to the infinity link to finish the piece and create an unexpected earring that would still look great with other silver jewelry. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
2 inches long
Compliments the Infinity Chain

name: Geometric Link with Green Amethyst
description:
These earrings are a great lightweight earring that has a hint of color but is not overwhelming, so it is easy to pair with other silver jewelry pieces. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and green amethyst
1.75 Inches long

name: Branch and Pearl Earrings
description:
These earrings are a unique juxtaposition of traditional materials and modern design with the use of pearls and cast branch elements. There is a long ear wire that compliments the long branch piece from the front. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
2 inches long 
These earrings look great with the Trinkety Pearl and Chain Necklace

name: Double Lavender Earrings
description:
These delicate earrings are inspired by Provence, France and the lavender I fell in love with while studying there. They create a unique silhouette but would still go great with other silver jewelry. I hand carved the pieces out of wax and then cast them in sterling silver. I then add champagne fresh water pearls, grey fresh water pearls, or blue mystique quartz. Be sure to message me what drop you would like. These create a beautiful and unique pair of earrings that go great with other silver jewelry.

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls or blue mystique quartz
2 inches long

name: Trinkety Pearl Chain Necklace
description:
Each component is carved from wax and then cast in silver. I then connected all the components to create a collected feel, as if you were walking threw nature picking up leaves, branches, and flowers. I then added pearls, one of my favorite materials. This creates a one of a kind necklace that would be a great addition to any jewelry collection. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
17 inches long (can be adjusted if requested
Goes great with my pearl post earrings

name: Organic and Pearl Pendant
description:
This pendant is inspired by the beach. It is carved from wax and then cast in sterling silver to create a totally unique pendant. It forms a soft and beautiful silhouette that is accented by a pearl. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearl
Can request either a 16 or 18 inch chain
Goes great with my pearl post earrings

name: Branch and Pearl Pendant
description:
This simple chain necklace takes a traditional pearl and dresses it up by giving it more character by dropping it off of a cast silver branch.  The "acorn" center piece is creative, unique, and simple enough to wear on a daily basis. 

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearl
Total length is 16 inches (can be adjusted if requested)
Can be paired with the Pearl and Link Earrings

name: Single Lavender and Grey Pearl Earrings
description:
These delicate earrings are inspired by Provence, France and the lavender I fell in love with while studying there. I hand carved wax and cast it in sterling silver to make these one of a kind earrings. They create a unique silhouette but would still go great with other silver jewelry because of the color of the pearl.

Materials: 
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
1.65 inches long
These earrings looks great with the Trinkety Chain Necklace

name: Branch and Pearl Chain Necklace
description:
This creative necklace combines natural inspiration with functionality. This branch pendant creates a unique center piece for a classic pearl and sterling silver chain.

Materials:
Sterling silver and fresh water pearls
17 inches long (can be adjusted if requested)
Goes great with Pearl and Link Earrings

name: Infinity Studs
description:
Sterling silver studs that complement the Infinity Chain. These simple earrings would be a great finishing touch to any outfit because of their simple yet unique design. 

Materials:
Sterling silver
.8 inches long
